### Local Image

~~~ .php
Image::from('.\path\to\photo.jpg')->crop(72)->saveAs('photo-2.jpg');
~~~

### Remote Image

~~~ .php
Image::from('http://example.com/photo.jpg')->crop(72)->saveTo('.\path\to\photo-2.jpg');
~~~

### Base64 Image

~~~ .php
Image::from('data:image/jpeg;base64,…')->crop(72)->saveTo('.\path\to\photo-2.jpg');
~~~

